headlights (an $80 option), a six-way memory driver seat (a $235
option) and door locks that automatically locked when the car was
shifted out of park (a $185 option).
   Needless to say, there was plenty of legroom, hip room, and head
room in this car in the front seats and ininess is what
this car is all about. The trunk, with 18.4-cubicf space
compared with 16 cubic feet in last year's model, was mnctive in today's
market where smaller cars dominate.
   Cadillac says compet
