<HEAD>Wendy's To Open In Persian Gulf</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DUBLIN, Ohio (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Wendy's International Inc. announced
Wednesday that it signed a franchise agreement with a Saudi Arabian
company to open 30 fast-food restaruants in the Persian Gulf over
the next five years.
   Under the deal with Mawarid Food Co. of Saudi Arabia, two
